        "image_border_radius": 0,
        "body_text": "<p>Here’s the unexpected part many women don’t talk about:</p><p><strong>When digestion feels better, everything else can start feeling better too.</strong></p><p>Many women say they notice:</p><p>✅ less heaviness after meals<br/><br/>✅ more confidence wearing fitted clothes<br/><br/>✅ <strong>feeling more comfortable in their body again</strong><br/><br/>✅ less stress around food and eating</p><p>Because when you’re not constantly thinking about your stomach after every meal, it can change how you feel day-to-day overall.</p>",
        "text_size": 18,
        "text_color": "#3b3b3b",
        "testimonial_text": "<p>💬 <em>“Gut Harmony has honestly made such a difference for me. I don’t feel uncomfortable after eating all the time anymore, and I </em><em><strong>feel much more confident going out to dinner or wearing clothes that used to make me self-conscious after meals.</strong></em><em>”</em> — <strong>Patricia</strong></p>",
